  urldate = {2024-04-14},
  abstract = {With the emergence and development of web extended reality (WebXR) application programming interface (API), WebXR currently provides a new display platform for virtual reality (VR), augmented reality (AR), and mixed reality (MR) technologies. This paper studies the combination of the Chinese traditional cultures and WebXR. What's more, we put forward the future vision of China's ancient Silk Road based on WebXR technology. This paper introduces a few achievements in the field of WebXR and also analyzes the main advantages of WebXR technology. In order to confirm that WebXR has a unique effect on the display of China's ancient Silk Road, this paper uses the A-Frame framework to conduct experiments. Analysis shows that this technology is particularly important today, and it has played a positive role in the digital protection of Chinese traditional culture. Although WebXR is still in its infancy, its advantages are obvious. Continuously develop and update WebXR technology, Chinese traditional culture can better take advantage of this technology to achieve major changes and improvements.},
